      "instruction": "<p>Peel and slice 1/4 of your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>red onion[s]</strong> as finely as you can and add it to a small bowl</p><p>Dice the <strong>remaining onion</strong> and <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Add you <strong>diced tomato</strong> to the bowl with the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato salad</strong></p>",
