            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, increase the heat to high and add your<strong> meat-free mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!)</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Tip: Try not to stir too often so the mince gets nice and brown!</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
