        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince is browned, add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further or until cooked through and fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
