    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince is done, add a squeeze of <strong>lemon</strong> <strong>juice</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spiced meat-free mince</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
